<div id="banner">
  <%= image_tag "PUPP.svg", class: "banner__image" %>
  <div class="banner__intro">
    Welcome to Pupp, the cuttest puppies are waiting to for you. Set play dates with any listed puppy. It doesn't matter if you're looking for joy or a cure for sadness, puppy cuteness is always the solution.
  </div>
  <button id=btn-5 >
    Choose a puppy
